achieves high performance closing to the optimal one\nmanually obtained by the user.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sun, 21 Oct 2018 14:18:03 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 19 Feb 2019 01:15:36 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-02-20"}
